info.title: Label Field Catalog â€’ Read
info.description: This service enables you to retrieve label field placeholders from your SAP S/4HANA system and use them in the process of designing label templates in external systems. The service contains all relevant information about a label field placeholder such as ID, version, and the group that it belongs to.

x-sap-shortText: Read label field placeholders using this synchronous inbound service

values.text: Product Compliance - Label Template Authoring Integration(SAP_COM_0772)
